      P("What are major themes in contemporary Chinese society visible in media and conversation?","Think urbanization, technology, and generational change.","Contemporary themes: (1) Urbanization — massive internal migration; 农村 (countryside) vs. 城市 (city); 留守儿童 (left-behind children whose parents migrated for work); (2) Tech innovation — 微信 WeChat, 支付宝 Alipay, TikTok (抖音 Dǒuyīn); digital economy; (3) Environment — pollution (雾霾 wùmái smog), clean energy push, carbon neutrality goals; (4) Belt and Road Initiative (一带一路) — global infrastructure investment; (5) Demographic challenges — aging population, declining birth rate after one-child policy; (6) Generational differences — 90后 (post-90s), 00后 (post-2000) generation with different values from parents. These themes appear in AP exam reading and listening materials.","hard"),
